  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/bf078f4c6e4d76499021b7c0d6a11ef5.poster.avif?t=1774131349\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/bf078f4c6e4d76499021b7c0d6a11ef5.webm?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/bf078f4c6e4d76499021b7c0d6a11ef5.mp4?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Casual Archery Puzzles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on archery escapades across a whimsical world following the adventures of five different protagonists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/3c6c19fc9edef5ec0efd5d49cfab582f.poster.avif?t=1774131349\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/3c6c19fc9edef5ec0efd5d49cfab582f.webm?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/3c6c19fc9edef5ec0efd5d49cfab582f.mp4?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handcrafted Levels With Unique Challenges</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer strategies for over 40 handcrafted stages and unlock achievements, characters and levels on your way to win the big tournament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/98cb6afdc0a4dad1c0c055eb4a581b2d.poster.avif?t=1774131349\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/98cb6afdc0a4dad1c0c055eb4a581b2d.webm?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/98cb6afdc0a4dad1c0c055eb4a581b2d.mp4?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quirky Dialogue</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stroll through walkable levels and connect with the locals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/0256317a1f7dd8383a99d5bc961e6046.poster.avif?t=1774131349\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/0256317a1f7dd8383a99d5bc961e6046.webm?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/0256317a1f7dd8383a99d5bc961e6046.mp4?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Little Slices of Life</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock cozy dioramas and charming lore through achievements and story progression.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/09b72b8c049cbd85f866ffb71bf06ab8.poster.avif?t=1774131349\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/09b72b8c049cbd85f866ffb71bf06ab8.webm?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523500/extras/09b72b8c049cbd85f866ffb71bf06ab8.mp4?t=1774131349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >___________________________________________________</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*If it matters to you: This is a <strong>completely human-made</strong> game :) No LLMs were used in its creation.</p>",
